messages.message: I'm trying to generate some prompt udf rules for field validations. It takes quite a long time and it would be good if (1) we could potentially add some auto-complete into the prompt udf rule text box and (2) make the code generation faster. I'd imagine the code that people are validating with is fairly simple

From clicking "run" (0:06) to code generating finishing (0:24) seems like a lot of time especially when running the validations itself is short. A better comparison may be extracting fields which is done fairly quickly

yeah our team owns this! :sweat_smile:

open to any suggestions on how to improve this
Are we upgrading the model we use for the code generation with Agent mode?
